                <h4>What is the voting age population of Burton, Ohio?</h4>
                <p>
                    The total voting age population of Burton, Ohio, meaning US citizens 18 or older, is 1,133.  The voting age population is 46.3% male and 53.7% female.
                </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Burton, Ohio residents are senior citizens?</h4>
                    <p>
                        According to the latest census statistics, 29.8% of
                        the residents of Burton are 65 or older.
                    </p>
                

                
                    

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    
                    
                    <h4>What are the racial demographics of Burton, Ohio?</h4>
                    <p>The racial demographics of Burton are 98.5% White and 1.5% Black. Additionally, 2.1% of the population identifies as Hispanic.</p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Burton, Ohio residents are below the poverty line?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Burton, 12.3% of
                    residents have an income below the poverty line, and the child poverty rate
                    is 12.8%.
                    On a per-household basis,
                    9.2% of families are below
                    the poverty line in Burton.
                    </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Burton, Ohio residents are in the labor force?</h4>
                    <p>
                    Among those aged 16 and older, 56.5% of
                    Burton residents are in the labor force.
                    </p>
                

                

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    

                
                
                <h4>What are the education levels among Burton, Ohio residents?</h4>
                <p>Among the adult population 25 years old and over,
                    86.9% of
                    Burton residents have at least a high school degree or
                    equivalent, 23.9%
                    have a bachelor's degree and 6.4%
                    have a graduate or professional degree.
                

                
                
                <h4>What percentage of Burton, Ohio residents speak a non-English language at home?</h4>
                <p>
                Among Burton residents aged 5 and older, 2.7% of them speak a non-English language at home.
                Broken down by language:
                2.3% of residents speak Spanish at home,
                0.2% speak an Indo-European language, and
                0.0% speak an Asian language.

                </p>
                

                
    


                
                
                    <h4>What is the unemployment rate in Burton, Ohio?</h4>
                    <p>
                        The unemployment rate in Burton is 8.3%, which is calculated among residents aged 16 or older who are in the labor force.
                    </p>

                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Burton, Ohio residents work for the government?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Burton, 17.9% of the
                    residents in the non-military labor force 
                    are employed by the local, state and federal government.
                    </p>
                

                

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    

                
                
                    <h4>What is the median income in Burton, Ohio?</h4>
                    <p>The median household income in Burton is $51,875.</p>
                

                
    


                
                
